    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>Mrch 13, 1862</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. I. M Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">In answer to yours of yesterday<lb/> I enclose the 2 following
                copies of receipts of yours<lb/> which will fully agree with my statement</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I am aware that we settled up to <date>March 1860</date><lb/> but in
                your letter (Copy No I) you will perceive that<lb/> on <date>Jan, 15 1861</date> you
                acknowledge receipt for payment;<lb/> and again in your letter No 2 dated
                    <date>August 14 1861</date><lb/> you again acknowledge receipt, which
                agrees<lb/> with the entries in my book. I trust you<lb/> will rectify your
                mistake.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I enclose also $3.00 for the insertions, which<lb/> will now settle
                all your claims on me. As soon as<lb/> I shall be in <placeName>Paris</placeName> I
                will inform you concern<lb/>ing the subscription for the future, for the present
                I<lb/> wish to make no engagement.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I have yet 3 Bibles and one <add>רכב וצלח</add><lb/> on hand which I
                will take with me, as you<lb/> proposed and try to sell them for you.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Thanking you heartily for your kind wishes</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Believe me my dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Yours truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">A Loewe</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Excuse the scribble, in haste.</p>
            <p rend="The following is written sideways in the left margin.">Please write me an
                answer</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. I. M. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>1227</placeName>
            </p>
